  "prompt": "I deleted my friend ID from WeChat. How do I find it again?",
  "response": "If you've deleted a friend ID on WeChat and want to find it again, here are a few steps you can try:\n\n1. **Search for the Friend's WeChat ID**: If you remember your friend's WeChat ID, you can search for it directly in the WeChat search bar.\n\n2. **Check Your Chat History**: If you've previously chatted with the friend, try looking for the conversation in your chat history. You may still be able to see their profile or WeChat ID in the chat log.\n\n3. **Look in Your Phone Contacts**: If your friend is saved in your phone's contacts and they have linked their WeChat account to that number, you can add them back to WeChat using the contacts feature.\n\n4. **Ask Your Friend**: If you are unable to recover the ID on your own, consider reaching out to your friend via another messaging app or means to ask for their WeChat ID again.\n\n5. **Scan a QR Code**: If you have access to your friend's QR code, you can scan it to add them back on WeChat. \n\n6. **Search Through Mutual Friends**: If you have mutual friends, you could check their contact lists or ask them to provide your friend's ID.\n\nUnfortunately, if you do not have any information about your friend's WeChat ID and the above methods do not work, it may be challenging to recover it.",
